</li></ul><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-40_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span>Additionally, adherence to guidelines from professional bodies like the General Medical Council (GMC) and Nursing and Midwifery Council (NMC) ensures that training meets the high standards required in healthcare.



  
